{"type":"message","id":"7fadbac2","parentId":"68b22af9","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:10:26.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 4geeksacademy.com website is a Next.js SPA that serves HTML for all routes - it's an SPA with client-side routing. The real API endpoints are likely on a different domain, or they're behind Next.js API routes that are compiled into the SPA bundle.\n\nLet me look at what the breatheco.de platform uses - that's where students actually code and do their work. Also let me check if there's a specific API for the learning platform.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Sa2LVFdFR5W7cPGtURTk4258","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try breatheco.de more thoroughly - this is the coding platform\nfor url in \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/api/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/api/v1/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/v1/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/api/me\" \\\n  \"https://breatheco.de/me\"; do\n  code=$(curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" \"$url\" -H \"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\" 2>&1)\n  echo \"$code $url\"\ndone\n\necho \"---\"\n# Check the SPA of breatheco.de too\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breatheco.de/\" 2>&1 | grep -oP 'src=\"[^\"]*\"' | head -10"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Try breatheco.de more thoroughly - this is the coding platform\\nfor url in \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/api/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/api/v1/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/v1/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/api/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://breatheco.de/me\\\"; do\\n  code=$(curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 -o /dev/null -w \\\"%{http_code}\\\" \\\"$url\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\\