{"type":"message","id":"11b87469","parentId":"155f3c52","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:11:54.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user seems to have just acknowledged. Let me re-approach the problem. They had the token in `.env` and want me to be able to connect to their 4Geeks account using it. \n\nSince Composio doesn't have a direct 4Geeks integration, I need to create a custom MCP server or a skill that wraps the 4Geeks API. But first, let me think about what the 4Geeks API actually is.\n\n4Geeks Academy uses a platform called \"BreatheCode\" - `breatheco.de`. Looking at the page source earlier, I saw:\n\n```\n\"BREATHECODE_HOST\":\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com\"\n```\n\nSo the real API is at `https://breathecode.herokuapp.com`. Let me try that with the token.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"text","text":"Buena, vamos a por el API real. EncontrĂ© en el bundle de breatheco.de que el backend estĂˇ en **`https://breathecode.herokuapp.com`**."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Dn2SfG4akGvNf0YOZO2h3834","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# This is the actual API host from the Next.js runtime config\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/v1/auth/me\" -H \"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | python3 -m json.tool 2>&1 | head -50"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# This is the actual API host from the Next.js runtime config\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/v1/auth/me\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\\\" -H \\\"Accept: application/json\\\" 2>&1 | python3 -m json.tool 2>&1 | head -50\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_VSTXKACseAEzSTeBtS6K7070","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test different API paths\nfor path in \"v1/auth/me\" \"v1/user/me\" \"v1/me\" \"v1/profile\" \"auth/me\" \"api/v1/auth/me\"; do\n  echo \"=== $path ===\"\n  curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/$path\" -H \"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | head -100\n  echo \"\"\ndone"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Test different API paths\\nfor path in \\\"v1/auth/me\\\" \\\"v1/user/me\\\" \\\"v1/me\\\" \\\"v1/profile\\\" \\\"auth/me\\\" \\\"api/v1/auth/me\\\"; do\\n  echo \\\"=== $path ===\\\"\\n  curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/$path\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\\\" -H \\\"Accept: application/json\\\" 2>&1 | head -100\\n  echo \\\"\\\"\\ndone\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782501105763,"responseId":"gen-1782501106-IOgbn8k3Ivq616Y3yztP"}}
