{"type":"message","id":"90423fc5","parentId":"a3d2d8a3","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:12:08.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The herokuapp endpoint is returning \"Not Found\" for all paths. This might be the old/deprecated API. The actual API must be somewhere else. Let me look at the 4Geeks platform more carefully.\n\nThe runtime config from breatheco.de showed:\n```json\n\"BREATHECODE_HOST\":\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com\"\n```\n\nBut that's returning 404. Maybe the API has moved or uses different paths. Let me try the 4geeksacademy.com SPA more carefully to see what API it calls.\n\nActually, looking at the \"NotFound\" response - it might just be that herokuapp is the API backend but it needs proper routing. Let me check the SPA request more carefully - maybe it calls different endpoints or uses different headers.\n\nLet me look at the 4geeksacademy.com SPA's Javascript more carefully for actual API calls.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"text","text":"El backend en Heroku parece estar caĂ­do o deprecated. Vamos a buscar el API real que usa la SPA de 4geeksacademy.com.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2b19dccac04b460d96f20c10","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if the API uses a different approach - maybe relative to 4geeksacademy.com subdomain\n# Let's look for actual fetch/XHR calls in the JS bundles\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 20 \"https://4geeksacademy.com/assets/index-CnPtc-59.js\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '(api|breath|4geeks|breathecode)[^\"'\"'\"',) ]*' | sort -u | head -30"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Check if the API uses a different approach - maybe relative to 4geeksacademy.com subdomain\\n# Let's look for actual fetch/XHR calls in the JS bundles\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 20 \\\"https://4geeksacademy.com/assets/index-CnPtc-59.js\\\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '(api|breath|4geeks|breathecode)[^\\\"'\\\"'\\\"',) ]*' | sort -u | head -30\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_736a6059867e41a6b54bc4ea","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test if the API is behind 4geeksacademy.com with an api subdomain\nfor host in \\\n  \"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/v1/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/auth/me\" \\\n  \"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/me\" \\\n  \"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/v1/user\" \\\n  \"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/user\"; do\n  code=$(curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" \"$host\" -H \"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\" 2>&1)\n  echo \"$code $host\"\ndone"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Test if the API is behind 4geeksacademy.com with an api subdomain\\nfor host in \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/v1/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/auth/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/me\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/v1/user\\\" \\\\\\n  \\\"https://api.4geeksacademy.com/user\\\"; do\\n  code=$(curl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 8 -o /dev/null -w \\\"%{http_code}\\\" \\\"$host\\\" -H \\\"Authorization: Token 6853e727ba8243e8fd4afef911953857f167a292\\\" 2>&1)\\n  echo \\\"$code $host\\\"\\ndone\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_29fde5e024d4408e874082ff","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Let's check what API the 4geeksacademy.com frontend actually calls\n# Check the response headers for API hints\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 -D - \"https://4geeksacademy.com/\" 2>&1 | head -20\necho \"===\"\n# Also try the staging/live URLs\nnslookup 4geeksacademy.com 2>&1"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Let's check what API the 4geeksacademy.com frontend actually calls\\n# Check the response headers for API hints\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 -D - \\\"https://4geeksacademy.com/\\\" 2>&1 | head -20\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\n# Also try the staging/live URLs\\nnslookup 4geeksacademy.com 2>&1\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782501118422,"responseId":"gen-1782501119-3cyozqsNVLRjAk7mfARp"}}
