{"type":"message","id":"2d3a1c57","parentId":"ae5cb247","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:12:17.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The 4geeksacademy.com website is an SPA (Single Page Application) hosted on Google Cloud. The API endpoints it calls are relative `/api/*` paths. However, those return HTML (SPA fallback), not JSON.\n\nThe actual backend at `breathecode.herokuapp.com` is returning 404 for all paths I've tried.\n\nLet me look more carefully at the JavaScript bundle to find how it calls the actual BreatheCode API. The Next.js config on breatheco.de had `BREATHECODE_HOST: \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com\"` but that's for the legacy breatheco.de platform.\n\nFor 4geeksacademy.com, the API might be different. Let me look deeper into the JS bundle to find the API calls.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d358ba4a5b84a65a8122d18","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Let me look deeper into the API calls in the main bundle\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 --max-time 25 \"https://4geeksacademy.com/assets/index-CnPtc-59.js\" 2>&1 | grep -oP 'https?://[^\"'\"'\"'` )}]+' | grep -v 'googleapis\\|googletag\\|facebook\\|twitter\\|cdn\\.' | sort -u | head -30"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Let me look deeper into the API calls in the main bundle\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 15 --max-time 25 \\\"https://4geeksacademy.com/assets/index-CnPtc-59.js\\\" 2>&1 | grep -oP 'https?://[^\\\"'\\\"'\\\"'` )}]+' | grep -v 'googleapis\\\\|googletag\\\\|facebook\\\\|twitter\\\\|cdn\\\\.' | sort -u | head -30\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782501129972,"responseId":"gen-1782501130-604m3W7LFQW8o7wv4UX9"}}
