{"type":"message","id":"f9e949f8","parentId":"3a6ca6c9","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:15:29.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API endpoints I can confirm working:\n- `v1/auth/user/me` - user profile (WORKING)\n- `v1/auth/user/{id}` - specific user by ID (WORKING)\n- `v1/auth/token/validate` - validate token (403, but it exists)\n- `v1/certificate/me` - certificates (WORKING)\n\nMany other endpoints return 404 (they probably need specific querystrings or auth level). That's fine, I have enough to build the skill with the core endpoints that work.\n\nNow let me look at the breathecode API repo on GitHub to find more endpoints.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5260a576f265487baa5c7584","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Let's check for more endpoints by looking at the API patterns from the JS\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 20 \"https://breatheco.de/_next/static/chunks/55850-774d1048dfae6958.js\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '[\"'\"'\"']/[a-z]+/[^\"'\"'\"']+[\"'\"'\"']' | grep -E 'v1|auth|cohort|assignment|mentor|event|student|profile' | sort -u | head -30"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Let's check for more endpoints by looking at the API patterns from the JS\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 20 \\\"https://breatheco.de/_next/static/chunks/55850-774d1048dfae6958.js\\\" 2>&1 | grep -oP '[\\\"'\\\"'\\\"']/[a-z]+/[^\\\"'\\\"'\\\"']+[\\\"'\\\"'\\\"']' | grep -E 'v1|auth|cohort|assignment|mentor|event|student|profile' | sort -u | head -30\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4cb10738c39c4227accaf0dd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if there's a newer API version or another base URL\n# Try the breathecode.herokuapp.com root to see if there's API docs or redirects\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | head -10\necho \"=== api docs? ===\"\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/docs\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | head -10\necho \"=== swagger ===\"\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger\" 2>&1 | head -10"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Check if there's a newer API version or another base URL\\n# Try the breathecode.herokuapp.com root to see if there's API docs or redirects\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/\\\" -H \\\"Accept: application/json\\\" 2>&1 | head -10\\necho \\\"=== api docs? ===\\\"\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/docs\\\" -H \\\"Accept: application/json\\\" 2>&1 | head -10\\necho \\\"=== swagger ===\\\"\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger\\\" 2>&1 | head -10\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782501318636,"responseId":"gen-1782501319-nbZaIXy6H5U2W3GT7r7O"}}
