{"type":"message","id":"4e5f2896","parentId":"d0b2aded","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:15:39.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Alright, I found the API! The BreatheCode API is at `https://breathecode.herokuapp.com` and it works. I've confirmed:\n\n1. `v1/auth/user/me` - returns user profile âś…\n2. `v1/auth/user/{id}` - returns user by ID âś…\n3. `v1/certificate/me` - returns certificates âś…\n4. `v1/auth/token/validate` - 403 (needs specific permissions)\n5. There's a Swagger docs at `/swagger` (returns HTML)\n\nNow I have enough to create the skill. Let me build it with the known endpoints and the script to wrap the API calls.\n\nLet me also check the swagger docs to find more endpoints.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"text","text":"Hay un Swagger en `/swagger`. Vamos a extraer los endpoints documentados."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_hd51CWKIpq1XFyfi7Tgw9413","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Extract swagger JSON\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | grep -oP 'url:\\s*\"[^\"]+\"' | head -5\necho \"===\"\n# Try swagger.json\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger.json\" 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport json,sys\ntry:\n    data = json.load(sys.stdin)\n    paths = list(data.get('paths',{}).keys())\n    print('\\\\n'.join(sorted(paths)[:40]))\nexcept: print('no json')\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Extract swagger JSON\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger\\\" -H \\\"Accept: application/json\\\" 2>&1 | grep -oP 'url:\\\\s*\\\"[^\\\"]+\\\"' | head -5\\necho \\\"===\\\"\\n# Try swagger.json\\ncurl -sL --connect-timeout 5 --max-time 10 \\\"https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/swagger.json\\\" 2>&1 | python3 -c \\\"\\nimport json,sys\\ntry:\\n    data = json.load(sys.stdin)\\n    paths = list(data.get('paths',{}).keys())\\n    print('\\\\\\\\n'.join(sorted(paths)[:40]))\\nexcept: print('no json')\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782501331484,"responseId":"gen-1782501332-aiIZgWEuEZFwbgoaDiZZ"}}
