{"type":"message","id":"698b1a93","parentId":"3edf5f9d","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:21:04.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'm ready to explain to the user what I've done and what's next.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_details"},{"type":"text","text":"Listo. AquĂ­ el resumen de lo que hice:\n\n---\n\n## âś… Skill `4geeks` creada\n\n**API identificada:** `https://breathecode.herokuapp.com/v1/`\n\n**ÂżQuĂ© hice?**\n- LeĂ­ tu token del `.env` â€” funciona, eres **Pedro Sanchez**, estudiante en **4Geeks Madrid** y **4Geeks.com**\n- CreĂ© un script wrapper en `skills/4geeks/scripts/4geeks_api.sh` que usa el token automĂˇticamente\n- DocumentĂ© los endpoints como skill (`skills/4geeks/SKILL.md`)\n- GuardĂ© todo en la memoria persistente\n\n**CĂłmo usarlo desde ahora:**\n\n```bash\n# Tu perfil (ya funcionando)\nbash skills/4geeks/scripts/4geeks_api.sh \"auth/user/me\"\n\n# Tus certificados\nbash skills/4geeks/scripts/4geeks_api.sh \"certificate/me\"\n```\n\n**Lo que descubrĂ­:**\n- No hay integraciĂłn directa vĂ­a Composio, asĂ­ que usamos un script shell nativo\n- Endpoints confirmados: `auth/user/me`, `auth/user/<id>`, `certificate/me`\n- El backend corre en Heroku y usa New Relic, el stack es Django REST\n\n**ÂżQuĂ© mĂˇs te gustarĂ­a poder hacer?** Cosas como:\n- Consultar tus cohorts / cursos activos\n- Ver tu progreso en assignments\n- Traer eventos/workshops disponibles\n- Integrar esto con un heartbeat para check-ins periĂłdicos\n\nDime quĂ© acciones te interesan y las agrego al script."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782501657389,"responseId":"gen-1782501658-zkSg9Z0bIOUXOFPODbDX"}}
